nodes.text: Alderaanian Oversea was a form of city construction that originated from Alderaan wherein cities were built on stilts in the shallow saline seas. A manifestation of Alderaanian desire to build their cities as a part of the environment, the concept was used in Tipoca City and many other stilt-cities on Kamino, although their stilts were significantly taller due to the much-deeper oceans on that world.
